Classification: Documentary
Genre: Buy, Sell & Trade | Family | Lifestyle
Status: New Series
Network: Channel 4 ( United Kingdom)

Jimmy and the Giant Supermarket is a documentary series which is broadcast on Channel 4. Jimmy Doherty wants to make free range food affordable for everyone and has challenged Britain's biggest supermarket, Tesco, to let him prove he can do it.
